snippet.title: Hate Me Not - #teaser
snippet.description:
Hello everyone, here is a teaser for our upcoming #1bit #top-down #shooter :)
We ported the game over from #unity3d to #godot and it feels like we are in the last mile, for publishing the game. 

If you want to try out the #demo version: 
https://notjustgames.itch.io/hatemenot
